            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515886657613-9f3515b0c78f?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop">

            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Designer Fabrics</h3>
                <p>
                    Explore stylish imported and branded fabrics for every special occasion.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521572267360-ee0c2909d518?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop">

            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Custom Tailoring</h3>
                <p>
                    Perfect fitting and premium finishing by experienced tailoring experts.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<section class="testimonials">

    <h2 class="section-title">Customer Reviews</h2>

    <div class="review-grid">

        <div class="review">
            <p>
                “Excellent collection and perfect stitching quality. Very professional tailoring.”
            </p>

            <h4>- Happy Customer</h4>
        </div>

        <div class="review">
            <p>
                “Best place in Bengaluru for wedding suits and premium fabrics.”
            </p>

            <h4>- Wedding Client</h4>
        </div>

        <div class="review">
            <p>
                “Timely delivery with superb fitting. Highly recommended.”
            </p>

            <h4>- Regular Customer</h4>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<section class="contact">

    <div class="contact-box">

        <h2>Visit Our Store</h2>

        <p>
            Vijayanagar, Bengaluru • Open Daily 10:30 AM – 9:00 PM
        </p>

        <a href="tel:+918023101934" class="btn btn-primary">
            Contact Store
        </a>

    </div>

</section>

<footer>
    © 2026 J M Textiles & Fashion • Designed with Premium Modern UI
</footer>

</body>
</html>
